data.description: Welcome to 143 Continental, a beautifully appointed residence in the heart of San Antonio. This delightful 4 bedroom, 2 bathroom home offers a perfect blend of comfort, convenience, and style. Step inside to discover an inviting interior designed to meet the needs of modern living. The open-concept layout seamlessly connects the living, dining, and kitchen areas, fostering an ideal space for gatherings and daily relaxation. Step outside to a generously sized backyard, ready to be transformed into your personal oasis. Whether you're enjoying a morning coffee on the patio or hosting gatherings, this outdoor space offers endless possibilities. This home is within close proximity to St. Mary's University, Our Lady of the Lake University and downtown San Antonio. Enjoy the convenience of easy access to shopping, dining, and entertainment options while still relishing a peaceful neighborhood setting. Don't miss the opportunity to make this charming property your new home. Schedule a showing today and experience the allure of 143 Continental firsthand.
